OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FA woman who claims she was abused by
OL,8,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson as a child has
OL,9,Fsaid the former DUP leader's wife "did
OL,10,Fnothing about it" after she informed
OL,11,Fher about one alleged incident.
OL,13,FComplainant A also rejected
OL,14,Fsuggestions by a barrister that she is
OL,15,F"making this up as you go along" in
OL,16,Frelation to the allegations.
OL,18,FEx-MP Jeffrey Donaldson, 63, has
OL,19,Fpleaded not guilty to 18 alleged
OL,20,Foffences.
OL,26,@qD@cOUrD@QO]wD@AOUwD@`O]
