PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FThe charges span a time period between
OL,8,F1985 and 2008 involving two alleged
OL,9,Fvictims.
OL,11,FEleanor Donaldson denies several
OL,12,Fcharges of aiding and abetting her
OL,13,Fhusband's alleged offending.
OL,15,FShe is facing a trial of the facts.
OL,17,FComplainant A, one of the two alleged
OL,18,Fvictims, has been giving evidence for
OL,19,Fa third day to the jury of seven men
OL,20,Fand five women at Newry Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
