PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson sat in the dock at
OL,8,Fthe rear of the courtroom, wearing a
OL,9,Fdark blue suit and taking occasional
OL,10,Fnotes.
OL,12,FComplainant A was cross-examined on
OL,13,FMonday by Ian Turkington KC, barrister
OL,14,Ffor Eleanor Donaldson.
OL,16,FThe barrister questioned her about why
OL,17,Fshe had not mentioned during her
OL,18,Fpolice interviews in 2024 all of the
OL,19,Fcounselling sessions she had received
OL,20,Ffollowing the alleged abuse.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FThe witness said she had "nothing to
OL,8,Fhide" and had forgotten to mention
OL,9,Fsome of the counselling.
OL,11,FMr Turkington referred to Complainant
OL,12,FA's use of the words "really foggy" in
OL,13,Fher police interview, relating to her
OL,14,Fmemories of some of the alleged abuse.
OL,16,FShe said: "Many people know with
OL,17,Fchildhood abuse there is an issue with
OL,18,Fmemory.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@EO]tD@VOUtD@cO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
