PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,F"I have tried to remember these events
OL,8,Fand convey them to the best of my
OL,9,Fability."
OL,11,FThe barrister referred to notes made
OL,12,Fby a counsellor following a session
OL,13,Fwith Complainant A, where he had
OL,14,Frecorded "Memory really poor, very
OL,15,Fbad".
OL,17,FHe said: "Which of those five words
OL,18,Fwould you not use?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]vD@JOUwD@DO]yD@JOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
