SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FShe said: "I knew by the look on her
OL,8,Fface she knew I was telling the truth.
OL,10,F"Why would I make something like that
OL,11,Fup? I had no motive. Once she
OL,12,Fidentified I was telling the truth,
OL,13,Fshe did nothing about it."
OL,15,FThe barrister then turned to an
OL,16,Fallegation made by the complainant
OL,17,Fthat Jeffrey Donaldson had kissed her
OL,18,Fand put his tongue in her mouth.
OL,26,@oD@KOUrD@AOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
