PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FThe barrister asked: "Are you making
OL,8,Fthis up as you go along?"
OL,10,FShe responded: "Absolutely not, I find
OL,11,Fit absolutely ridiculous that you
OL,12,Finfer that."
OL,14,FThe barrister then referred to an
OL,15,Fincident where she alleges Jeffrey
OL,16,FDonaldson rubbed her chest with his
OL,17,Fhand under her clothing.
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@YO]rD@POUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
