CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FThe court previously heard a claim
OL,8,Ffrom the complainant that Eleanor
OL,9,FDonaldson had witnessed the incident
OL,10,Fbut did not intervene.
OL,12,FPressing her on the details of the
OL,13,Falleged incident, the barrister said
OL,14,Fshe was "spectacularly backtracking"
OL,15,Fin her evidence.
OL,17,FHe said: "You are making this up as
OL,18,Fyou go along."
OL,20,FShe said: "That is your assumption...
OL,21,FI am here to tell the truth."
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@dO]yD@JOUzD@NO]|D@KOU}D@]O]
