OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780419953
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson 'did nothing'
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged abuse incident,
OL,5,Ccourt hears
OL,7,FThe trial continues.
OL,9,FJeffrey Donaldson, a former long-
OL,10,Fstanding MP for Lagan Valley, was
OL,11,Farrested and charged at the end of
OL,12,FMarch 2024.
OL,14,FHe resigned as DUP leader and was
OL,15,Fsuspended from the party after the
OL,16,Fallegations emerged.
OL,18,FWeeks before his arrest, he had led
OL,19,Fthe DUP back into devolved government
OL,20,Fat Stormont after a two-year boycott
OL,21,Fof the powersharing institutions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
